	]em
	", and 
	[em 
		(__wikiLink|displaytext=Super Mario Bros. 3|href=/17G)
	]em
	". In addition, new mechanics means 
	(__wikiLink|displaytext=new glitches|href=/GameResources/GB/DonkeyKong)
	", which are readily used in a TAS in the interest of speed.
	$LF
]div
